SOLAR·ARCH — Bioclimatic Solar Analysis Tool

Concept & Thermal Comfort Methodology
    Arq. Gerardo Velázquez Flores
    The thermal comfort analysis methodology, including the adaptive comfort
    temperature bands and bioclimatic classification system implemented in
    this software, is the intellectual contribution of Arq. Gerardo Velázquez
    Flores. This concept forms the analytical core of the tool.

Design, Development & Implementation
    Joshua Abdiel Barragán Guardado
    All software design, code architecture, frontend and backend development,
    3D visualization, solar geometry engine, and overall technical
    implementation are the work of Joshua Abdiel Barragán Guardado.

